id="110356488025922357921-about-page" class="o-xc-Sya tSa" role="tabpanel" aria-hidden="false"><div class="i4c Bn"><div><div class="Cec rga"><div class="lib" style="width: 520px;"><div class="ona Fdb bsa" style="width:900px"><div class="Ypa jw Yc am"><div id="10" class="Ee ZPa vna WRa" role="article"><div class="ZYa ukoEtf"><div class="Lqc"><div class="F9a">我的故事</div><div class="miIoOb Cdmn9d"></div></div></div><div class="Uia"><div class="kec Iqc"><div class="wna Phb"><div class="Cr">個性宣言</div><div class="y4">Try to Keep everything in Mind</div></div><div class="wna xRb"><div class="Cr">自我介紹</div><div class="y4"><p>Michael is a master student of BAEIR Lab at National Taiwan University. His research interests include Information Retrieval, Data / Text / Web Mining, Machine Learning, Natural Language Processing and Data Mining for BigData. He is also a programmer or a web developer.</p><p>He loves to take participate in technology conference occasionally to keep learning new things. Michael thinks the world where everyone has the power to share knowledge, so he got involved with trying to keep everything in his blog.</p><p><i>Skill keywords: Ruby, Java, Web development, python, data mining, R, Hadoop, Angular.js</i></p><div><br></div></div></div></div></div><div class="Iqc"></div></div><div id="9" class="Ee h5a vna Jqc" role="article"><div class="ZYa ukoEtf"><div class="Lqc"><div class="F9a">教育背景</div><div class="miIoOb Cdmn9d"></div></div></div><div class="Uia"><div class="lec Iqc"><div class="wna"><div class="y4"><ul class="Kla"><li class="UZa"><div class="PLa">台灣大學</div><div class="ija">資訊管理學研究所, 2013 - 目前所在公司/機構</div><div class="ija">國立台灣大學資訊管理學研究所, 資訊分析與經濟效果研究實驗室
